<article>
<h1>Ben Cartwright: Man of the Ponderosa</h1>
Ben Cartwright is the respectable, polite, and formal Man of the Ponderosa.
He has three young men, each from a different mother, Adam, Eric(Hoss),
and Joseph.

Adam seems the closest to him, as Joe and Hoss are the mischeivous ones,
but all his sons are loyal and favor his word.

